Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.65,0:03:20.48,Captions-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(980,0)\pos(956,745)\fnRoboto Bold\bord0\blur0.8}A terra de Poverty, Hungeria\NIlha Lazy Bones
